Nigerian singer-songwriter Adekunle Gold is off to a good start in 2022, he has released a new single entitled, Mercy. The record was produced by Blaise Beats. Basking on the success of Davido-assisted number “High,” Adekunle Gold displays no sign of slowing down. Although he is one of the hottest Nigerian artists of 2021, the singer promises a better 2022. RELATED: Simi feat. Joeboy – So Bad Adekunle Gold starts the year on a good note as he renders his first official single for the year. The song is titled “Mercy,” it features Simi‘s sultry adlibs and it is highly impressive. As regards the production, his partner in crime Blaise Beat claims the credit.  Digital Streaming Platforms The post LISTEN: Adekunle Gold Releases New Single ‘Mercy’ appeared first on NotjustOk. Receive top breaking news, events, ideas, and more!